Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.19,0:00:04.32,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:19.19,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:31.27,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.27,0:00:32.78,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Here, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:38.06,Main,Akiopapa,0,0,0,,Akio...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:41.06,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.43,0:00:48.90,Main,Akiopapa,0,0,0,,I moved here \N soon after you left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.39,0:00:50.78,Main,Akiopapa,0,0,0,,It’s been three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:54.15,Main,Akiopapa,0,0,0,,Have you been doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.48,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,Do you think \N I could stay for a few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:01:00.04,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,I came to search for herbs \N in the Snow-White Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:08.10,Main,Akiopapa,0,0,0,,You’re still pretending \N to be a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.59,0:01:24.27,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:27.12,Main,Shimaboshi,0,0,0,,We don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:31.79,Main,Shimaboshi,0,0,0,,It’s happened several times recently. \N Something might be happening in the forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:35.95,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,A Pokémon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:38.86,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,It’s hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:43.98,Main,Villager,0,0,0,,Wait! Stay in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.78,0:01:56.23,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,Somebody, please...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:59.11,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Why are you closing the gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:00.86,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Shouldn’t we go help it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:02.96,Main,Villager,0,0,0,,Get back inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:04.68,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,But it’s hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:06.53,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,We should help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:17.06,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,I believe there are other \N injured Pokémon in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:18.72,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,Won’t someone please join—?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:22.23,Main,Villager,0,0,0,,Why should we \N have to help Pokémon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:23.85,Main,Villager,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:27.13,Main,Villager,0,0,0,,It’s {\i1}their{\i0} fault we can’t go \N into the forest, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:30.47,Main,Villager,0,0,0,,Yeah! It’d be much better \N if those monsters just disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:32.60,Main,Villagers,0,0,0,,Yeah, that’s right!{Will split into different lines for whatever's audible. - Toa}{"aaa sou da sou da!" is literally the only line I can fully make out here. -TL}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:36.35,Main,Shimaboshi,0,0,0,,We, the Security Corps, will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:37.95,Main,Villager,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:40.46,Main,Shimaboshi,0,0,0,,We are not going there \N to help the Pokémon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:44.25,Main,Shimaboshi,0,0,0,,But it’s undeniable that \N something strange is happening in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:47.06,Main,Shimaboshi,0,0,0,,We need to investigate \N for the village’s safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:03.31,Main,Akiopapa,0,0,0,,Why are you \N so fixated on Pokémon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:06.17,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:07.81,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:12.60,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,I want to understand them.{the Pokémon.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:25.16,Main,Akiopapa,0,0,0,,You can’t walk in the snow \N with shoes like those.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:29.70,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:31.25,Main,Villager,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:33.85,Main,Villager,0,0,0,,Don’t do anything{ too} reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:56.77,Main,Shimaboshi,0,0,0,,You’re not scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:03:58.81,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:00.40,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,There’s somebody I’d like to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.38,Main,Security Corps Person,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:26.25,Main,Security Corps Person,0,0,0,,The heavens are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:27.61,Main,Security Corps Person,0,0,0,,When did...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:45.72,Main,Shimaboshi,0,0,0,,Follow him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:00.44,Main,Security Corps Person,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.47,Main,Shimaboshi,0,0,0,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:07.83,Main,Shimaboshi,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:19.19,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,They’re protecting their young...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.17,Main,Shimaboshi,0,0,0,,It’s too dangerous! \N Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:31.38,Main,Shimaboshi,0,0,0,,Come back! \N What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:40.31,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,I want to give this \N to the little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:48.78,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,I know it’ll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:05:58.35,Main,Akiopapa,0,0,0,,Akio!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.20,Main,Security Corps Person,0,0,0,,The Pokémon are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:17.55,Main,Shimaboshi,0,0,0,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:38.83,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,We should get them \N to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.46,Main,Shimaboshi,0,0,0,,We’re not equipped to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:02.56,Main,Security Corps Person,0,0,0,,There’s something weird here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:03.60,Main,Security Corps Person,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:06.35,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,All of you, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:08.82,Main,Shimaboshi,0,0,0,,No! You’re coming with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:13.61,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:19.19,Main,Security Corps Person,0,0,0,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:20.17,Main,Security Corps Person,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.98,Main,Shimaboshi,0,0,0,,Hurry! \N We have to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:27.48,Main,Security Corps Person,0,0,0,,What’s going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:34.64,Main,Shimaboshi,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:41.29,Main,Akio,0,0,0,,My friend... \N came for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:05.58,Main,Akiopapa,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:09.27,Main,Akiopapa,0,0,0,,...don’t know why you’re \N so fixated on Pokémon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:19.27,Main,Akiopapa,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:22.81,Main,Akiopapa,0,0,0,,Perhaps you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:38.31,Main,Akiopapa,0,0,0,,Come visit once in a while.
